```
Without Snipara:
  User: "Explain the auth system"
  → RLM reads ALL files (500K tokens)
  → Hits LLM token limits
  → Expensive, slow, often fails

With Snipara:
  User: "Explain the auth system"
  → RLM calls snipara.context_query("auth system")
  → Snipara returns 5K tokens of RELEVANT context
  → Fast, cheap, accurate
```
